          <td class="mainbody">

<span class="headers">Neriak Troll Shadow Knight (Dark Basher's) Armor</span>
<p>
<p>Hail Kugaran at neg 353 neg 434 in the Neriak Foreign Quarter, near the bank. </p>

<p>Kugaran says 'Whut yoo want from Kugaran! Unless yoo [Shadowknight] yoo leave me alone.'</p>

<p>You say, 'I am a shadowknight'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'I don't know if I should trust yoo but I suppose I can let yoo prove yerself. If yoo are [interested] in helping me wit gadaring some tings and [creating yer own armor] yoo let Kugaran know.'</p>

<p>You say, 'I am interested in creating my own armor'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'Well den I guess we get started. Dere isn't much to tell besides dat yoo will have to go out and collect [various items] fer yer armor materials. First tings first go ahead and take yer assembly kit now, it is in here dat yoo will put da items yoo collect to make yer armor material. Once yoo have da material yoo can use it wit da right mold I gib yoo to make yer armor.'</p>

<p>*** Receive Dark Bashers Armor Assembly Kit ***</p>

<p>You say, 'What various items'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'Dere are lots of tings yoo will need. Once yoo are ready I can gib yoo da mold fer Dark Basher's [Helms], [Bracers], [Armguards], [Boots], [Greaves], [Gauntlets] and [Breastplates]. When yoo are ready to make a piece yoo tell me which piece you [wish to craft] and I gib yoo da right mold.'</p>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft helms'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer helm material yoo will need to combine 2 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 1 Bone Chip, 1 Fire Beetle Eye and 1 Water Flask in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Helm.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Helm Mold ***</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Helm<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: HEAD<br>
AC: 5<br>
INT: +1 AGI: +2<br>
WT: 4.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft bracers'</p>
<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer Bracer material yoo will need to combine 1 Brick of Crude Bronze, 2 Snake Scales, 1 Ruined Bear Pelt and 1 Bottle in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Bracer.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Bracer Mold ***</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Bracer<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: WRIST<br>
AC: 4<br>
INT: +1 AGI: +3<br>
WT: 2.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft armguards'</p>
<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer armguard material yoo will need to combine 2 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 1 Halfling Blood, 1 Cracked Helm of da Lifebringer and 1 Short Ale in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Armguards.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Armguard Mold ***</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Armguards<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: ARMS<br>
AC: 5<br>
INT: +1 AGI: +2<br>
WT: 3.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft boots'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer boot material yoo will need to combine 3 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 1 Giant Wood Spider Femur, 1 Shadow Wolf Pelt and 1 Ration in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Boots.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Boot Mold ***</p>


<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Boots<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: FEET<br>
AC: 5<br>
INT: +1 AGI: +2<br>
WT: 3.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft greaves'</p>
<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer greaves material yoo will need to combine 4 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 2 Ruined Wolf Pelts, 1 Fire Beetle Leg and 1 Mead in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Greaves.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Greaves Mold ***</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Greaves<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: LEGS<br>
AC: 6<br>
INT: +2 AGI: +2<br>
WT: 3.5 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft gauntlets'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer gauntlets material yoo will need to combine 3 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 1 Snake Egg, 1 Black Mamba Skin, and 2 Bat Wings, in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Gauntlets.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Gauntlet Mold ***</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Gauntlets<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: HANDS<br>
AC: 5<br>
INT: +1 AGI: +3<br>
WT: 4.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'I wish to craft breastplate'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'To create yer breastplate material yoo will need to combine 5 Bricks of Crude Bronze, 1 Calcified Sternum, 1 Zombie Skin, 1 Halfling Ribcage, 1 Spider Legs and 1 Orc Skull in yer assembly kit. Once yoo have created da proper material take it to a forge along with this mold to fashion yer very own Dark Basher's Breastplate. Return to me for one [final task] I have to ask of yoo after yoo have completed yer breastplate.'</p>

<p>*** Receive An Enchanted Breastplate Mold ***</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Basher's Breastplate<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: CHEST<br>
AC: 12<br>
STR: +2 INT: +3 AGI: +5<br>
WT: 5.0 Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You say, 'What final task'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'Da task is to get me a few [important items] that I need for me studies. If yoo go get dem I give you nice shiny ting.'</p>

<p>You say, 'What important items'</p>

<p>Kugaran says 'Me needs 1 Burned Out Lightstone, 1 Halfling Clavicle and 2 Cracked Helms of the Lifebringer. Bring me these tings and I give yoo nice reward.'</p>

<p>Hand him all of the above and he gives you:</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Dark Bashers Two-Handed Sword<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: PRIMARY<br>
Skill: 2H Slashing Atk Delay: 43<br>
DMG: 12<br>
Bane DMG: Undead +2<br>
INT: +3 MANA: +10<br>
WT: 10.0 Size: LARGE<br>
Class: SHD<br>
Race: TRL</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Totals for the armor:<br>
AC: 36<br>
INT: +11<br>
AGI: +22<br>
STR: +2<br>
WT: 26.5</p>

<p>SUMMARY:</p>

<p>Helm -<br> 
2 bricks of crude bronze (kill orcs in Nek forest) <br>
1 bone chip <br>
1 fire beetle eye <br>
1 water flask </p>

<p>Bracers - <br>
1 bricks of crude bronze <br>
2 snake scales <br>
1 ruined bear pelt <br>
1 bottle (merchant bought) </p>

<p>Armguards - <br>
2 bricks of crude bronze <br>
1 halfling blood (no drop, stackable - drops off of Nek halflings) <br>
1 Cracked Helm of the Lifebringer (rare drop off human priests at pos 1000 pos 1000 - no drop and stackable) <br>
1 short ale (merchant bought) </p>

<p>Boots - <br>
3 bricks of crude bronze <br>
1 giant wood spider femur (larger Nek forest spiders) <br>
1 shadow wolf pelt <br>
1 ration (merchant bought) </p>

<p>Greaves - <br>
4 bricks of crude bronze <br>
2 ruined wolf pelts <br>
1 fire beetle leg <br>
1 mead (merchant bought) </p>

<p>Gauntlets - <br>
3 bricks of crude bronze <br>
1 snake egg <br>
1 black mamba skin <br>
2 batwings (sold in chanter guild but trolls might not have enough faction) </p>

<p>Breastplate - <br>
5 bricks of crude bronze <br>
1 calcified sternum (rare drop off calcified skels?) <br>
1 zombie skin <br>
1 halfling ribcage (very rare drop from "Questgiver" halfling) <br>
1 spider legs <br>
1 orc skull (off any orcs in Nek Forest) </p> 

<p>Final Task - <br>
1 burned out lightstone <br>
1 halfling clavicle (very rare?) <br>
2 Cracked Helms of the Lifebringer </p>

<p>ASSEMBLY ITEMS:</p>

<p>Dark Bashers Armor Assembly Kit, WT 10, Cap 10, Size LARGE, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Helm Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Bracer Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Armguard Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Boot Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Greaves Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Gauntlet Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP<br>
An Enchanted Breastplate Mold, WT 0.4, Size SMALL, MAGIC, LORE, NO DROP</p>

<p>SHOPPING LIST:</p>

<p>21 Bricks of Crude Bronze<br>
1 Bone Chips<br>
1 Fire Beetle Eye<br>
1 Water Flask<br>
4 Snake Scales<br>
2 Ruined Bear Pelts<br>
2 Bottles<br>
1 Halfling Blood<br>
3 Cracked Helms of the Lightbringer<br>
1 Short Ale<br>
1 Giant Wood Spider Femur<br>
1 Shadow Wolf Pelt<br>
1 Ration<br>
2 Ruined Wolf Pelts<br>
1 Fire Beetle Leg<br>
1 Mead<br>
1 Snake Egg<br>
1 Black Mamba Skin<br>
2 Bat Wings<br>
1 Calcified Sternum<br>
1 Zombie Skin<br>
1 Halfling Ribcage<br>
1 Spider Legs<br>
1 Orc Skull<br>
1 Burned Out Lightstone<br>
1 Halfling Clavicle</p>

<p>All the items can be found in Nektulos Forest or bought from shops.</p>

<p>Crude bronze - drops from Deathfist Orcs<br>
Halfling blood - NO DROP and is a common drop from any halfling<br>
Lightbringer helms - NO DROP and are fairly common drops from the Rodcet Worshippers (around /loc 1000 1000)<br>
Bottles, Short Ale, Ration and Mead - all store-bought<br>
Halfling Clavicles and Ribcages - rare or very rare drops off of halflings, one ribcage came off of a halfling called Stitch at the halfling temple (around /loc -1000 1000). One clavicle came off of one of the halflings at the halfling stump<br>
Calcified Sternum - NO DROP, very rare, one eventually dropped from a greater skeleton. Might be more common drop off of the skeletons in Kithicor.</p>

<p>The look of the armor is a brown plate, the sword is a very plain 2H sword (looks like a rusty 2H sword).</p></p><p>
